snippet.title: Battle Craze: The First Trailer
snippet.description:
http://kelexo.thedailypos.org/batcrazeb/

Battle Craze is an indie fighting game in development by Team Craze, emphasizing animation and character in a world much like ours. Our proof of concept is here in IKEMEN GO before we move onto something greater. Please, download, play and tell us what you think!

http://battlecraze.shoutwiki.com/wiki/Main_Page
